$interpreted: Sophie: Hutchinson, is the cable support ready!?
Hutchinson: Everything is all set.
Hanbei: Let me through, let me through! Time to perform!
Hanbei: Ouch!! Who the hell's just standing there like a zombie?
Rune: ...it's Rune.
Hanbei: Heyy!! You dirty little──
Sophie: Hanbei! Now's not the time to argue!
Ru-yi: Ohh, noooo~ Sophie ~ my...my ball is missing~
Sophie: Missing!? Wasn't it in the box last time...
Sophie: OW!! Ouch!! My butt...
Ru-yi: Sophie! Are you okay?
Ru-yi: *sob*...*sob*...it's all my fault~~
Sophie: Ru-yi, don't cry. The tent is going to fill up with your tears!
Rune: Sophie...command...
Sophie: What?
Rune: Rune is waiting for a command.
Sophie: Rune, I don't want to order you around.
Rune: ...Rune...needs an order.
Hanbei: Sophie! The performance is about to begin──
Hanbei: There's water everywhere!?
Hutchinson: Sophie, the audience has already begun to enter the venue!
Sophie: Already? Okay, I'm going!
Sophie: Rune, I'm sorry. Can you help me clean this up?
Rune: Order...received...clean up.
Sophie: Thank you! After we're finished with the performance we'll come help!
Happy Child: Mommy! The circus is fun~ Can we come tomorrow~
Kind Lady: Ok, ok, ok. Mommy will bring you back tomorrow.
Happy Child: The whale spits water and the pricky animal──
Rune: Uhh...
Drunk Hooligan: Hey, look at this fellow here. He's been sweeping this whole darned area.
Arrogant Hooligan: This is a long street. Is he gonna sweep the whole damn thing?
Drunk Hooligan: Well if he ain't got a brain problem, then he's a gosh darn fool!
Arrogant Hooligan: Hehehe...
Arrogant Hooligan: Hey, this boy don't say a darn word.
Drunk Hooligan: Maybe there's something wrong with him?
Arrogant Hooligan: Hey! He's just a non-speaking dummy!
Drunk Hooligan: Get that broom outta my face!
Arrogant Hooligan: Where you going! I'm not done with you!
Rune: Rune...must sweep...it's Sophie...order.
Rune: Move...
Arrogant Hooligan: I ain't moving! What're you gonna do about it!?
Arrogant Hooligan: Hu...how's he this strong!?
Drunk Hooligan: N-n-n-no, no! Don't come any closer! We were wrong!
Arrogant Hooligan: Sorry! We're sorry!
